node.title: Person dead after 'incident' At Anzac Bay on Saturday
node.description: Another person was also treated for minor to moderate injuries.
node.content: ["A person is dead after \"an incident\" at Anzac Bay in Bowentown on Saturday night.\u00a0\n", "Emergency services were called shortly before 9pm. ", "Police say another person was also treated for minor to moderate injuries.", "\"Police are making enquiries in relation to the death on behalf of the Coroner, who will release their finding in due course.\"\u00a0"]
